 He also pays about 20,000 yen ($177) per month for it; he doesn't need heating, but in the summer the bill increases to 24,000 yen ($213). Given the fire risk, he also has high homeowner's insurance. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2017-02-03/japanese-video-rental-store-owner-has-truly-insane-gaming-setup/.111697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.animenewsnetwork.com%2Finterest%2F2017-02-03%2Fjapanese-video-rental-store-owner-has-truly-insane-gaming-setup%2F.111697&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b7123fa6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2017-02-03/japanese-video-rental-store-owner-has-truly-insane-gaming-setup/.111697</a></blockquote><br />\n唔會overheat著火咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff3ab4a2471a678866af90bfa3ba95129ddc5ab","tid":107184,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"咁正都有hater比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好整齊好撚正，男人嘅遊戲天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be0e3b3a3b7ad1a21c9acb69b6e58a813d9c258","tid":107184,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"mmorpg同時玩10個acc<br />\n會唔會成個公會都係自己玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0715c71dbd3c065983d0e809940c45c4c00754b2","tid":107184,"uid":49678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有錢買屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地直情係起屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有塊地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"